Run
This command is used to download software, packages. This will create additional layers on top of base image
ex: apt-get install unzip curl htop wget npm httpd python






CMD
Sets default command and parameters which can be overwritten from the command line
ex: CMD has comand mentioned in docker file. This can be overwritten from CLI like docker run -it ......command
When the docker container runs




ENTRYPOINT

This will always be executed wont be replaced from CLI
If you want to replace this use docker run -it --entrypoint=sleep 5




You can use combination of CMD and ENTRYPOINT for one command to be executed and other to be replaced





